				<div class="jumbotron">
					<h2 class="display-4" style="font-family: sans-serif;color: #F012BE;">Safety Tips for Women</h2>
					<hr class="my-4">
					<h5 style="color: #85144b;">Criminals often tend to view women as being more vulnerable and softer targets than men. Don’t be an easy victim and constantly educate yourself on ways to stay safe. Start off with these safety tips for women</h5>
				</div>
